dataBase.sentence: You know my aunt Minnie is so ill...
How could I know if I'm a good person?
My house feels so empty now...
I think I offended my pastor...
Wait, do I have a purpose?
You know my dad was an alcoholic?
Is there an afterlife for real, or...?
When did I start getting old?
I don't think my kids like me...
I might have anxiety for real...
